# Customer Segmentation using RFM and K-Means

## 🎯 Objective
To group customers based on purchasing behavior.

## 🧠 Approach
- Data Cleaning
- RFM Analysis (Recency, Frequency, Monetary)
- Data Scaling
- K-Means Clustering

## 📊 Key Insights
- High-value customers contribute most revenue
- At-risk customers have stopped purchasing
- Loyal customers buy frequently

## 💡 Business Recommendations
- Reward high-value customers
- Re-engage at-risk customers
- Maintain loyalty programs

## 🚀 Conclusion
Segmentation helps businesses target customers effectively and increase revenue.
